org.ensembl.driver
Interface CoreDriver

All Superinterfaces:
EnsemblDriver
All Known Subinterfaces:
Driver
public interface CoreDriver
extends EnsemblDriver

Provides adaptors for accessing to ensembl core databases.

Drivers are created and, where needed, should be initialised() before any of the getXXXX() methods are called.

See Also:
CoreDriverFactory
